 就打000000 或 N/A<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0aQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=6ce53e12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"b4ef8a1a00ee2eb268ef0282bc8cf4d5bf137722","tid":1478644,"uid":27518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:30:05.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d5602a43e5a60127dc322184a1e97bf11f958042","tid":1478644,"uid":292053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:30:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ca74817b4e9b959a9c351cd4c4115c4388a91a2c","tid":1478644,"uid":47337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7b42a08a943433de05bce389a186055bca3e29","tid":1478644,"uid":16740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:39:19.000Z","msg":"幫手推呀兄弟<br />\n只要取消左班港共官員外國户藉<br />\n佢地就唔會咁有恃無恐咁賣港"},{"pid":"a76be5bd6b56cfced748e2c17c7dca9d4fde6b6c","tid":1478644,"uid":79602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:39:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7866f3d680a796e79026de651632b461f389b410","tid":1478644,"uid":16740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:40:55.000Z","msg":"幫手推呀兄弟<br />\n只要取消左班港共官員外國户藉<br />\n佢地就唔會咁有恃無恐咁賣港"},{"pid":"06eb83b6c90dc08c9595d261d1173ebcc9d04b49","tid":1478644,"uid":16740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:41:13.000Z","msg":"幫手推呀兄弟<br />\n只要取消左班港共官員外國户藉<br />\n佢地就唔會咁有恃無恐咁賣港"},{"pid":"2e20e537094d7b42aa12cff622dc7c1be2365cd6","tid":1478644,"u